-- SUMMARY STATISTICS
-- Total entries: 130
-- Materials covered:
--   - Carbon Steel (mild/A36): 10-30mm at 1-20kW (O2, N2, Air)
--   - Carbon Steel Grade 50 (A572/S355): 10-30mm at 3-10kW (O2)
--   - Stainless Steel 304: 10-30mm at 2-12kW (N2, Air)
--   - Stainless Steel 316L: 10-30mm at 2-12kW (N2)
